00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,440
Long, curvy and meaty.

322
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,600
The humble hot dog is easy-to-make

323
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:03,440
and provides a tasty package
of carbohydrates and proteins.

324
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:06,600
But recently, heated on-line debate
has sprung up

325
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:09,320
about the proper way to
savour a sausage,

326
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:12,160
with some resorting to outright
saucy remarks.

327
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:16,440
Recently, discussions on
on-line hot-dog-enthusiast group,

328
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:19,240
Do Not Cross The Yellow Line,
got really heated

329
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:22,040
when a local café
started offering ketchup

330
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:24,120
as a condiment option for hot dogs.

331
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:27,480
It is understood that members of
Do Not Cross The Yellow Line

332
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:29,480
have strong beliefs about mustard

333
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:32,960
being the only sauce used
to dress hot dogs,

334
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:35,120
and do not condone the use of ketchup.

335
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:40,680
According to the National Hot Dog
and Sausage Council of the United States,

336
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:44,320
ketchup is not an advisable
condiment for hot dogs.

337
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:48,280
You see, we prefer the
time-honoured traditions of using

338
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,840
mustard, relish,

339
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,200
cheese, chilli,

340
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:53,080
onions for hot dogs.

341
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:56,680
We are simply trying to ensure
that this meat dish,

342
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,200
that we know and love,

343
00:16:58,200 --> 00:17:02,720
is best appreciated as it was
originally created. Right?

